high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and walk towards the door then turn left towards the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Slice the tomato in the green can under the counter.
Turn right then turn left towards the green can again.
Put the knife inside the green can.
Step to your left and face the can again
Take a tomato slice out of the can.
Turn around and walk to the white table behind you.
Put the tomato slice in the pan on the white table.
Pick up the pan from the table.
Turn around an walk towards the round black table then turn left and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the pan on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with the cut tomato on the counter.

high_descs: Walk towards the counter
Grab the knife from the counter
Walk with the knife towards the coffee machine
Cut the apple on the bottom of the counter
Walk towards the table and come back to the counter
Slice the apple on the bottom of the counter
Walk away and come back to the counter
Grab a slice of the apple
Walk with the slice of the apple towards the white table
Put the slice of the apple on the pan
Take the pan from the counter
Walk with the pan towards the stove counter
Put the pan next to the stove on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice an apple, grab a slice put it in the pan

high_descs: Turn around to go to the counter on the left of the stove.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Turn around to go to the front of the coffee maker.
Cut the tomato in the green container under the coffee maker.
Move over to right slightly.
Split the cut tomato in half.
Move over to left slightly.
Take out one slice of tomato
Turn around and go to the white table on the opposite side.
Place the tomato on the brown square pan on the table.
Pick up the pan with tomato in it.
Turn right and go to the stove.
Place the pan with tomato in it on the counter on the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with sliced tomato in it on the counter
